{"tid":2125920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「波波吧」疑爆親乳頭感染武肺","createTime":"2020-07-26T13:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T14:07:27.000Z","uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f52651228b24fc5765db165a0ed24525fc95c46","tid":2125920,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"有日本傳媒報道，札幌一種稱為「おっぱいパブ（《立場》譯﹕波波吧）」的性工作場所，猜測女員工乳頭疑因被受感染人士親吻，導致其後親吻同一乳頭的客人受感染。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該文並稱，服務員每小時可接待數名客人，每天接待人數可達 30 到 40 名，兩周內接觸客人數可達&nbsp;600 名。<br />\n<br />\n事件令不少網民討論被舔過的乳頭應否清潔消毒。有日本博客解釋，由於頻繁使用酒精消毒乳頭會令乳頭變乾，甚至破皮出血，因此服務員不會這樣做。然而事件爆發後，札幌紅燈區部份店舖已貼出<span class=\"red\">「全店乳頭徹底消毒」</span>的公告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文入去睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93-%E6%B3%A2%E6%B3%A2%E5%90%A7-%E7%88%86%E8%A6%AA%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84-%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AA%E6%BB%BF-30-%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%2593-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%2590%25A7-%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584-%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25BB%25BF-30-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=3ba48288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%2593-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%2590%25A7-%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2584%259F%25E